{"tid":667581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【把移民趕出美國】川普：一些移民是畜牲","createTime":"2018-05-17T01:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T02:46:12.000Z","uid":147314,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"133e9787b25a43eba4dc67de290615f0318bceea","tid":667581,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:12:11.000Z","msg":"把移民趕出美國 川普：一些移民是畜牲<br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2018/05/17 08:55 最新更新：2018/05/17 08:55<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓16日綜合外電報導）美國總統川普（Donald Trump）今天討論邊界築牆和執法時，形容一些移民是「畜牲」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，川普告訴造訪白宮的加利福尼亞州共和黨人說：「有人進到國內，或試圖進入，我們要把這些人趕出這個國家。」<br />\n<br />\n「你不會相信這些人有多糟糕，他們不是人，他們是畜牲，我們要把他們趕出這個國家。」<br />\n<br />\n川普在討論移民和執法、也就是所謂移民「庇護城市」和拉丁美洲街頭幫派MS-13後，發表這番言論。"},{"pid":"62d66f91228ab32dc316bd5199099f7d7a993c40","tid":667581,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:12:41.000Z","msg":"川普經常以「惡毒」和「殺手」來形容MS13成員。他們是源自美國的幫派，但大多為薩爾瓦多裔。川普經常將移民與這個幫派混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n川普這番最新言論，隨即招致民主黨人批評。<br />\n<br />\n科羅拉多州國會議員波利斯（Jared Polis）說：「移民是人。不是畜牲，不是罪犯，不是毒販，不是強暴犯。他們是人。」<br />\n<br />\n加州州長布朗（Jerry Brown）說：「川普在移民問題上說謊，在犯罪問題上說謊，在有關加州法律上說謊。」（譯者：葉俐緯/核稿：盧映孜）1070517<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201805170024-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201805170024-1.aspx&d=QZGlUmFjcFsXdRC5pcKbX%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1ead1531\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201805170024-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"6f78d015173cfc2f31bf8a0b76aa5ab46e150ddc","tid":667581,"uid":132524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2118b3f6f3ec22e1c459e59049a7d3c288029efa","tid":667581,"uid":92603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"川普：一些移民是畜牲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 : 全部移民不是畜牲，蝻同蝗都係昆蟲"},{"pid":"28b89ea0f5586e2b8f7c55df953419da826226d6","tid":667581,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"衰過畜牲<br />\n畜牧都唔係偷呃搶騙啦"},{"pid":"ad263c1550c61a8887c0ee1d4a8b98b2bb5c624a","tid":667581,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:50:55.000Z","msg":"Trump says some unauthorized immigrants 'aren't people' but 'animals' who will be rapidly kicked out of the US<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/trump-illegal-immigrants-animals-ms-13-california-sanctuary-cities-2018-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-illegal-immigrants-animals-ms-13-california-sanctuary-cities-2018-5&d=QZGlUmFjcFsXdRC5pcKbX%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=eb21e615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.businessinsider.com/trump-illegal-immigrants-animals-ms-13-california-sanctuary-cities-2018-5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06b2eaac532ffc15c689358a4c894cfba169316","tid":667581,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:51:49.000Z","msg":"鄰國人連畜牲都不如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ff70598c1ed629b26146071e931d3dd36d0f5f","tid":667581,"uid":40049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.illegalaliencrimereport.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/MS-13-Gang-Members-Getty-640x480.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.illegalaliencrimereport.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FMS-13-Gang-Members-Getty-640x480.png&h=699fedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nms13：多謝美國既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83964348d0919e48e1c5f288bdd09568e23a3bd","tid":667581,"uid":104699,"like":2,"di